   /* Abigail*/

"AbigailRosalieRamp": "I think walking into the saloon with my combat boots will be a little easier now with the ramp.",
"AbigailRosalieArrivalCT": "I like Rosalie's hair ribbon! I wonder where she got it?",
"Abigail.RosalieEmilyWalkCT": "I saw Rosalie the other day. She seemed to be struggling to walk up the hill past my place.$2 #$b# I thought of offering to get her wheelchair for her, but I didn't realize how much of the town is uphill. So it likely wouldn't have helped her...",
"Abigail.RosalieGeorgeWCCT": "It must be nice to be a ghost. You don't need to worry about if you can go somewhere based on your abilities...$2 $#e#There is the possibility ghosts are stuck in the place they died... So maybe not...$2",
"Abigail.RosalieVOTVJobEventCT": "I wonder if Rosalie will interview me about the ghosts in the graveyard. Their stories need to be heard too!",
"Abigail.RosaliesStoryCT": "So, I'd never ask Rosalie or George what happened to make them disabled...$2 #$b# Do you think the same rule applies to the dead?$1",
"Abigail.RosaliesFlareUpEventCT": "Sometimes I wonder if my parents would have been better off divorced...$s #$e# I know people talk about staying for the kids, but it only hurts them more...$s",
"Abigail.RosalieRadioEventCT": "So, @, what's it like being famous now that you were interviewed by The Voice of the Valley?",

"Abigail.RosaliesRibbonCT": "I may have to ask Rosalie if I can have one of her ribbons too! It looks so cute on Jas!$1",
"Abigail.DreamsAndDisastersCT": "I don't think there's anything wrong with two friends becoming more, right?",
"Abigail.RosaliexShane": "$query !PLAYER_NPC_RELATIONSHIP Current Alex Dating Engaged Married#Shane's come a long way from brooding in the corner. Now he has a gorgous girlfriend!$1 #$e# See, Sebastian?$5|Next time my mom tells me I can't change someone, I'm going to point at Rosalie and Shane.$1",

"Abigail.RosalieTheWinterMermaidCT": "I knew it! I KNEW there was something about Rosalie's voice!$7 #$b# Oh... You meant at the Night Market...$2",
"Abigail.RosalieTheWinterMermaidCT_OneDay": "%Abigail has that look, like you just told her Santa doesn't exist.",





/*Alex*/
"AlexRosalieArrivalCT": "I heard the new girl was an actress from the city. #$b# Maybe she was a plus size model? #$b# What? It's a compliment!$h",
        "Alex.RosalieEmilyWalkCT": "I saw the new girl trying to walk up the hill the other day. It's nice to see she's getting some exercise.",
        "Alex.RosalieGeorgeWCCT": "I should have known my Grandpa would do this the minute the new girl showed up in the wheelchair.$5 #$e# I see Grandpa's point, you shouldn't use something if you don't need it, but I mean... the doc wouldn't say she did if she didn't, right?$2",
        "Alex.VOTVJobEvent": "Grandma listens to the radio all the time, it's so cool that the plus size model is also there too!",
        "Alex.RosaliesFlareUpEventCT": "The plus size model is getting a divorce?!$u #$e# I wonder who cheated on who?$h",
        "Alex.RosalieRadioEvent": "I'm bummed I missed the live event, but at least we can hear her anytime we want just by talking to her!$1 #$e# I heard she sings on the beach on rainy days. Elliott's probably probably thrilled he gets a free concert.$1",
       
        "Alex.ShaneRosalieLowDayCT": "I've been seeing Rosalie and the Joja Mart guy together a lot lately. It's weird.$2 #$b# He's probably in it for the free alcohol. But what's she getting out of it?$2 #$e# Rosalie can do so much better! I mean, look at her!$2",
        "Alex.RosalieShaneSecondFirstKissCT": "Things are weird in town lately... Any idea why? #$b# I probably just need to work out more!$1",
        "Alex.RosaliexShane": "$query !PLAYER_NPC_RELATIONSHIP Current Alex Dating Engaged Married#What?! How on earth did-?! But she's-!$6 #$e# I give them a week!$1",
        "Alex.RosalieTheWinterMermaidCT": "Wow... That new girl... The Night Market Mermaid... Who knew?",

/*Caroline*/
"CarolineRosalieArrivalCT": "I heard that Rosalie moved somewhere by the ocean when she and her family left. #$b# I hope Pierre doesn't start stocking sea food...$s",
"Caroline.RosaliesFlareUpEventCT": "Pierre is too stingy to think about getting a divorce. Besides, I wanted Abigail to grow up with both of her parents.",

"Caroline.RosalieShaneSecondFirstKissCT": "$query !PLAYER_NPC_RELATIONSHIP Current Abigail Dating Engaged Married#Well, I hope that Abigail doesn't get any ideas about ruining her friendship with Sebastian.|This is why I told Abigail to wait for the person to bring a bouquet to you. #$b# Sometimes... it's better not knowing...$s",

"Caroline.RosalieTheWinterMermaidCT": "Don't tell Abigail about the new mermaid.",


/*Clint*/
"ClintOnRosalieRamp": "Don't tell Gus, but I did think that the stairs into the saloon were a bit steep.",
"ClintRosalieArrivalCT": "Rosalie and I didn't talk much as kids. I doubt that'll change. #$e# We used to hang out sometimes, but not much...",
"Clint.RosalieEmilyWalkCT": "I heard Rosalie and Emily are friends... Do you think she'd put in a good word for me to Emily?$1",
"Clint.RosalieVOTVJobEventCT": "I never used to get why my dad would listen to the radio while working, but I think I get it now.",
"Clint.RosaliesFlareUpEventCT": "Rosalie is single?!$u #$b# Uh... I mean...$s #$b# That's too bad... Poor Rose...$s",

"Clint.ShaneRosalieChildhoodTalkJasCT": "I didn't realize that the boy Rosalie used to hang out with in the summers was Shane. #$b# I don't expect her to remember we used to take the bus to and from school together every day until she moved...$2",
"Clint.RosalieShaneSleepOverCT": "Rosalie seemed to be doing okay the other night, but Shane wasn't doing so good.$2 #$b# Last I saw, he was asking Gus and Emily to take over for Rosalie. #$e# Maybe I'm not as observant as I ought to be...$2",
"Clint.RosaliexShane": "*sigh* Should have expected Rosalie and Shane to start dating when she came back.$2 #$e# I guess I hoped she would remember me and give me a chance...$2",


/*Demetrius*/
"DemetriusRosalieArrivalCT": "It's interesting how some people dress up in styles from the past. #$b# I prefer to look to the future myself.$h",
"Demetrius.RosalieGeorgeWCCT": "Have you ever seen a cat who is unable to use all their hind limbs climb a tree? #$b# It's amazing how easily they're able to adapt. #$e# They don't know that they're any different. #$b# If only humans could be that adaptable.",
"Demetrius.RosaliesFlareUpEventCT": "Did you know that true lifelong monogamy is rare in the animal kingdom? #$b# Monogamy is less about romance and more of a practical survival strategy. #$b# I suppose some humans think the same way.$1",

"Demetrius.RosaliexShane": "Did you know that over the first ten years of marriage, the chance of a divorce is 32%. #$b# For high school and childhood sweethearts who marry, it's 54% chance they'll divorce within the same timeframe.$2 #$b# However, those who wait to marry or reconnect later in life, have a much lower rate. #$e# I think Rosalie and Shane will be fine.$1",

/*Dwarf*/
"DwarfRosalieArrivalCT": "I thought I heard a siren's call this morning...",

/*Elliott*/
"ElliottRosalieArrivalCT": "I heard that Miss Rosalie was an actress, but she told me she's also a writer.#$b# Leah also said she's an artist. And Gus said she's a singer. #$b# I can't imagine one person having that many passions, but it's inspiring! #$b# Then again, maybe that's what's taking a toll on the rose.$s",
"ElliottRosalieArrivalCT_OneWeek": "That which we call a rose, by any other name would smell as sweet.$l #$b# Oh, I'm sorry, I've been reading the classics lately.$h",
"Elliott.RosalieGeorgeWCCT": "It's unfortunate that we always think of some stories as a work of fiction. #$b# I just wish Rosalie hadn't been the prime example of it.$a",
"Elliott.RosalieVOTVJobEventCT": "If having a simpler life by the ocean wasn't relaxing enough, I now have a radio to listen to our local celebrity.$1 #$b# It's so much less distracting than watching television.",
"Elliott.RosaliesStoryCT": "I did some of my best writing when I was isolated five years ago. #$b# Would I be horrible to say I missed it?$2",
"Elliott.RosaliesFlareUpEventCT": "I know Rosalie thought she found her fairytale ending,$s #$b# But the story wouldn't be as interesting if she didn't have some trials to overcome.$h #$e#I do hope she's doing alright, though...$s",
"Elliott.RosalieRadioEventCT": "Many don't know that in the original story of 'the Little Mermaid',$s #$b# She is unable to walk on land without feeling like knives were going through her new legs.$s #$b$ Maybe there's some truth to the rumours and Miss Rosalie's condition. #$e# I certianly believe.$h",

"Elliott.RosalieDreamsAndDisastersCT":"Shane and Rosalie's relationship make for quite the interesting story. #$b# Though I will admit, quite predictable... too predictable...$2 #$e# I hope if things are platonic, they're on the same page about that.$2 #$b# But it wouldn't make an interesting story if they were.$h",
"Elliott.RosalieShaneSecondFirstKissCT1": "I see this kind of thing in romance novels all the time. #$b# It's obvious that one of them kissed the other. #$b# It's hard to tell how they feel about it though... It could go either way...$2",
"Elliott.RosalieShaneSecondFirstKissCT2": "Did you know that forcing a kiss on someone, though romanticised throughout history, is really a form of assult.$s #$b# It *can* be romantic if both parties share feelings,$h #$b# But if not, it's just assult...$s #$e# How dare you?! I'm a writer! Researching the law and staying current is important!$a",

"Elliott.RosalieTheWinterMermaidCT": "It's facinating when fantasy immitates reality, don't you think @?",

/*
Emily
*/
"EmilyRampEventCT": "Gus left to go help his niece and left me in charge as soon as the ramp was done being installed. #$b# He seems a bit stressed, but no less excited for her to move in!$1 #$e# I don't think that Gus has taken a single day off since opening the saloon. It's sad his one day off is due to an emergency...$2",
"EmilyRosalieArrivalCT1": "Gus' niece, Rosalie, is so sweet! I think we're going to be best friends already!",
"EmilyRosalieArrivalCT2": "Huh? What? Nothing.$6 #$e# Did Haley say something?$5",
"Emily.RosalieEmilyWalkCT": "I feel so relaxed after going to the spa. #$b# But I wish Rosie could have joined me...$2 #$e#I hope she knows that there's nothing wrong with needing to cancel.$2 #$b#But she's so hard on herself...$2",
"Emily.RosalieGeorgeWCCT": "Rosie's been low since what happened with George.$u #$b# I hope it doesn't discourage her from going out...$s",


"Emily.RosaliesRibbonCT": "I had no idea that Shane and Rosie were childhood friends! It's such a small world! #$e# Though I do wonder why they didn't speak until now though...$2",
"Emily.RosalieSneezeEventCT": "I've seen Rosie's sneezes cause a flare before, but never so bad that she collapsed.$2 #$b# I hope she's doing better now...$2",
"Emily.RosalieSneezeEventCT_TwoWeeks": "I don't think I've ever seen Shane smile as much as he does around Rosie. #$b# It's amazing to see how much his personality changes when he's around her!$1",
"Emily.ShaneRosalieLowDayCT": "Rosie was so worried about Shane. I don't blame her given what he almost did before you stepped in.$2",
"Emily.RosalieDreamsAndDisastersCT1": "Shane is always looking at Rosalie to make sure she's doing okay when he's here at the saloon. #$b# It's really sweet how much he cares about his friend. #$e# I like to think that Rosie would tell me if she liked Shane in that way. Or Shane would if he did.$3",
"Emily.RosalieDreamsAndDisastersCT2": "Don't bring up Shane and Rosalie to my sister... She's not... acting like herself.$2 #$e# Why? No reason.",
"Emily.ShaneRosalieKitchenLoveCT": "Shane's been acting weird with Rosie around lately...$2",
"Emily.RosalieShaneSecondFirstKissCT": "I think Rosie and Shane had a fight...$s #$b# I thought she'd talk to me about it, but she's been really tight lipped and Shane hasn't come in.$2 #$b# I thought Rosie and I were close enough to talk about this kind of thing...$2",
"Emily.RosaliexShane": "I just knew the moment that Shane and Rosie looked at each other that they were meant to be together! #$e# I've never seen another couple so happy!$1",
"Emily.RosalieTheWinterMermaidCT": "Rosie is our Night Market Mermaid! I knew we were best friends for a reason!$1 #$e# I always go to the beach to look for mermaids, I should have known that there was one who was working with me at the saloon!$1",

/*
Evelyn
*/
"EvelynRampEventCT": "I heard that Gus had a ramp installed at the Saloon! #$b# Maybe George and I will pay a visit!$h",
"EvelynRosalieArrivalCT": "It's so nice to see Rosalie again after all this time! #$b# Now... Was she the first or second born to the nurse?",

"Evelyn.RosaliesFlareUpEventCT": "Back in my day, if things didn't work out between a married couple, you just stuck it out. #$b# George and I may not seem like it, but we still love each other dearly. #$b# I hope Rosalie can find that, and find peace.",
"Evelyn.RosaliexShane": "I saw the Rose and the chicken boy holding hands earlier today. How wonderful! #$e# After everything they've been through, they deserve something that lasts.",
"Evelyn.RosaliexShane_oneyear": "I wonder when Miss Rosalie and her sweetheart are going to have children? #$b# I'm sure they'd be adorable! I hope I'm around to see it!",


/*
George
*/
"GeorgeRosalieRamp": "So, I'm finally allowed to enter the saloon? #$b# Took 'em long enough.$5",
"GeorgeRosalieArrivalCT": "Rosalie was a thorn in my side! #$b# She always stuck sticks in my wheelchair, and disobeyed her mother! #$b# Yoba must be on my side to stick her in one, too! Heh heh!$h #$e# Wait... was she the quiet one?$s #$b# Oh... yes. She'll be fine.$h #$b# As long as she stays away from the drunk.",
"George.RosalieGeorgeWCCT": "How was I supposed to know the girl had chronic pain? #$b# She should have just said so!#$e#I know what that's like... I should probably apologize...$s#$b#...tomorrow.$h",

"George.RosaliesFlareUpEventCT": "I'm lucky that when I became disabled, Evelyn stayed with me. Made sure everything in the home was accessable.$s #$b# If Rosalie's husband couldn't do that, good riddence to him and good on her for kicking that leech to the curb.$h #$e# I'm sure that boy she was always with is dancing with joy now that the news is out.",

"George.RosaliexShane": "So, the little rascals who put wheels in my wheelchair are finally giving it the old college try. Took 'em long enough. #$e# I think her father owes me twenty gold. That was a lot back in our day.$1",


/*
Gil
*/
"Gil.RosalieRadioEventCT": "They say the siren has returned... #$b# The radio waves aren't safe as long as she's here.",


/*
Gus - i18n in the Gus JSON
*/ 


/*
Hayley
*/
"HaleyRosalieArrivalCT1": "The new girl has an... interesting asthetic...$3",
"HaleyRosalieArrivalCT2": "%Haley's mind is elsewhere",
"HaleyRosalieArrivalCT3": "Huh? What? Nothing!$2 #$b# Stop bugging me! I don't know anything!$3",
"HaleyRosalieArrivalCT4": "%Haley is not looking at you",
"HaleyRosalieArrivalCT_oneweek": "Rosalie is pretty...$2 #$b# Pretty... weird.$3",

"Haley.RosaliesFlareUpEventCT": "Rosalie was married, and now she isn't?!$8 #$b# Oh no... how terrible...$2",

"Haley.RosalieDreamsAndDisastersCT": "%Haley is muttering to herself. #$e# (Maybe if I give her some wine... or something...)$2 #$e# (Why would she go for *Shane* when her soulmate is so much better!)$3 #$e# (I don't know why Emily isn't helping, this is her thing!)$5 #$e# (I have to tell her! I just have to! There's no other way!)$3 #$e# (Sure, it'll break the kid's heart but she'll get over it!)$2 #$e# Oh! @!$2 #$b# Um... shopping... hair... la la la...$1",
"Haley.RosalieShaneSecondFirstKissCT": "I thought I'd be happy about something like this happening... But I'm not...$2",
"Haley.RosaliexShane": "Well... I guess the heart wants what it wants... and they *do* make a cute couple...$2 #$e# I never say this but... Emily was right. All this stress is going to give me crows feet.$3",

"Haley.RosalieTheWinterMermaidCT": "I didn't know they were casting for a new mermaid.$8 #$b# Did the casting director come here? I would be a much better choice?$3",


/*
Jas
*/ //IN SHANE's file//


/*
Jodi
*/
"JodiRosalieArrivalCT": "I wonder if Gus' niece is the same 'Rosalie' that's carved into Vincent's wall from when we moved. #$b# That would be a fun coincidence!$h",
"Jodi.RosalieVOTVJobEventCT": "It's so nice that I can just listen to 'The Voice of the Valley' and I don't need to worry about forgetting anyone's birthday!",
"Jodi.RosaliesFlareUpEventCT": "I can't imagine what Rosalie is going through with the divorce.$s #$e# When Kent and I got married, we didn't know each other for very long. #$b# It's a shame that things didn't work out for her after thirteen years...$s",

"Jodi.RosaliexShane": "I always wondered why Shane never seemed interested in dating anyone. I thought maybe Jas was keeping him from considering it. #$b# But I guess he was just waiting for Rosalie to come home.$1",

/*
Kent
*/
"KentRosalieArrivalCT": "Gus says his niece moved away from here because of the war... #$b#Similar circumstances brought us here from the city.",
"Kent.RosaliesFlareUpEventCT": "Divorce always brings out the worst in people. #$b# I'm lucky not to know first hand what it's like.",

"Kent.ShaneRosalieChildhoodTalkJasCT": "Rosalie's a good kid. I like that she always keeps an eye out on Jas and Vincent.$1",
"Kent.RosaliexShane": "When I was in the trenches, it was seeing Jodi, Samson, and Vincent again that kept me hopeful. #$e# Rosalie and Shane seem to have gone through a war of their own. It's good that they have each other.$1",

/*
Krobus
*/
"KrobusRosalieArrivalCT": "The rose has thorns...",

/*
Leah
*/
"LeahRosalieArrivalCT": "I heard Gus' niece dabbles in art. #$b# Looks like I may have some competition!$h",

"Leah.RosaliesFlareUpEventCT": "I've been terrified of getting carpel tunnel since I started sculping more seriously.$2 #$b# I can't imagine not being able to do what brings you joy because your body denies you.$2",

"Leah.RosalieDreamsAndDisastersCT1":"I honestly don't think I've ever heard Shane laugh before, and now it's all I've been hearing when Rosalie's around. #$b# It's nice, but a bit distracting when I'm working on my sculptures...$s",
"Leah.RosalieDreamsAndDisastersCT2": "If Rosalie and Shane are just friends, I say we believe them. #$b# Men and women can absolitely be friends and have it stay platonic!$h #$b# And if it's not, it's none of our business, right?",

"Leah.RosalieShaneSecondFirstKissCT": "I... may have seen something the other night at the ranch...$s #$b# I don't know how to ask Rosalie if she was okay with it, but I think it was mutual?$s #$b# I talked to Elliott about it and he didn't exactly give me advice on how to approach it...$s #$e# I will say, Rosalie and Shane really know how to argue.$s #$b# They wouldn't be able to if they didn't feel so strongly about each other, right? #$b# I mean that platonically or romantic.$h",

/*
Lewis
*/
"LewisRosalieRamp":"Rosalie was always a bit of a strange child. Quiet. Except when around her family and... never mind.",
"LewisRosalieArrivalCT1": "It's good to see folks come back to their roots.$h #$b# As they say, there's no place like home!$h",
"LewisRosalieArrivalCT2": "Well, it seems Rosalie has grown up to become a beautiful young lady!$h #$b# It's really too bad she gained all that weight though.$h",
"Lewis.RosalieGeorgeWCCT": "I understand where George is coming from. But that doesn't make what happened between him and Rosalie right.",
"Lewis.RosaliesFlareUpEventCT": "It's unfortunate that Rosalie ended up marrying the wrong man. #$b# The process in the city isn't as easy as it is here in Pelican Town.",


/*
Linus
*/
"LinusRosalieArrivalCT": "Rosalie gave me some interesting food last night that was off menu.$h #$e# She's also a wonderful baker, offered to make me a birthday cake!$h",
"LinusRosalieArrivalCT2": "I heard Rosalie singing as she cleaned the saloon last night. #$b# She sang a song my grandmother used to sing as a child... #$b# I... forgot about it until I heard it again...$2",

"Linus.RosalieGeorgeWCCT": "I know that my lifestyle isn't for everyone. #$b# I'm very lucky to be physically able to live the life I choose.",

/*
Marnie
*/    //In SHANE's file//


/*
Maru
*/
"MaruRosalieArrivalCT1": "I had no idea that Gus' niece was also a person of colour! #$b# It's nice to have something in common with her already!$h",
"MaruRosalieArrivalCT2": "Harvey's been... weirdly distracted lately...$s #$e$It's like he's trying to remember something but doesn't know what...$s", 

"Maru.RosaliesFlareUpEventCT": "I knew there was something going on with Rosalie, but she never let on what it was.$s #$b# I was surprised Harvey knew. I guess that explains why she was always here. They shared a secret.$s #$e# I hope she knows that we're behind her, and she has our support. #$e# My mom can sometimes mean well, but say the wrong thing... I'm sure Rose knows that though.",

"Maru.RosalieDreamsAndDisastersCT1": "Either Harvey misses Rosalie dropping off coffee, or the company with it.$s",
"Maru.RosalieDreamsAndDisastersCT2": "I've caught Harvey looking toward the saloon when he thinks no one's looking.$2",
"Maru.RosalieDreamsAndDisastersCT3": "The first time Rosalie came into the clinic, I had to pick up her jaw off the floor when she saw Dr Harvey.$1 #$b# She's still friendly with him, but less interested in his interests. #$b# I think he misses that...$2",
"Maru.RosalieDreamsAndDisastersCT4": "Rosalie says that she and Shane are just friends, but looking at them, I don't know if either of them are getting the memo.",

"Maru.RosalieShaneSecondFirstKissCT1": "$query PLAYER_NPC_RELATIONSHIP Current Maru Dating Engaged Married #Don't worry, my mom isn't going to do anything! #$b# Though I guess you've been warned if we broke up.$h|Don't worry, my mom isn't going to do anything. #$b# It's just a weird joke!$h",
"Maru.RosalieShaneSecondFirstKissCT2": "Harvey's been weird since Rosalie arrived, but he's been especially weird lately...$2",
/*
Pam
*/
"PamRosalieRamp": "I guess Gus adding the ramp goes to show that his customers are old timers like me!$h",
"PamRosalieArrivalCT": "We live in a town everyone wants to leave, but end up coming back to. #$e#It's too bad the kid didn't make it...$s",

"Pam.RosaliesFlareUpEventCT": "Rosalie is getting a divorce, huh? #$b# Good for her! Marriage isn't for everyone, and it's better she's out now while she's young!$h #$e# She's lucky she doesn't have kids though. That always makes it tough...$s",

"Pam.RosalieShaneSleepOverCT": "I could have sworn the other night that I saw Shane take Rosalie to the back... I don't remember him coming back out.$s #$b# If I didn't know he was sober, I would have thought they were up to something else. #$e# I know they're friends, but you can't be friends with the opposite sex without someone getting the wrong idea!$1",

"Pam.RosalieDreamsAndDisastersCT": "Don't go telling anyone I said this, but I think Shane goes to the saloon just to see Rosalie. #$e# She's real pretty, hope he doesn't get his hopes up too high!$1",

"Pam.RosalieShaneSecondFirstKissCT": "It's weird not seeing Shane and Rosalie together at the saloon. I thought the two were thick as theves.",

/*
Penny*/
"PennyRosalieArrivalCT": "Jas has been a bit upset lately... I hope things are okay at home.$s",
"PennyRosalieArrivalCTShaneSober": "Jas has been a bit upset lately...$s #$b# I hoped things would be better since Shane cut down on his drinking...$s",

"Penny.RosaliesFlareUpEventCT": "I'm sure Rosalie had a good reason not to stay married. Life's too short to be with someone who makes you unhappy. #$e# I do miss my dad sometimes, but my parents were miserable together...$s",

"Penny.RosalieDreamsAndDisastersCT": "Jas has been so happy since Rosalie and Shane have been spending time together.",

"Penny.RosalieShaneSleepOverCT": "$query PLAYER_GENDER Current Female #My mother has a strange belief that you can't be friends with the opposite sex. #$b# I'm sure Rosalie and Shane are just friends, and if they want to be more, it's not for us to say!$1|My mother has a strange belief that you can't be friends with the opposite sex. But you and I are just fine, right? #$b# I'm sure Rosalie and Shane are just friends, and if they want to be more, it's not for us to say!$1",

"Penny.RosalieShaneSecondFirstKissCT": "*sigh* I hate seeing Jas so upset again...$s",

/*
Pierre
*/

"PierreRosalieRamp": "Ah, a new customer to rip off! #$b# I hope she doesn't expect me to give her a discount just because she's Gus' niece!$h #$b# Did I say that outloud?$s",
"PierreRosalieArrivalCT": "I hope Rosalie grew up to be like her mother. #$b# And by that I mean she doesn't complain about my prices!$h #$b# Her father on the other hand...$3",
"Pierre.RosaliesFlareUpEventCT": "Rosalie's family must be going through it with the divorce...$s #$b# All that money for the wedding... just down the drain like that...$s",

"Pierre.RosalieShaneSecondFirstKissCT": "It's a good thing we don't do returns on certain items.",

/*
