*/
"RobinOnRosalieRamp": "I'm so excited to see Rosalie again! #$b# I hope the ramp shows she has people who care about her!$h",
"RobinRosalieArrivalCT1": "Have you had a chance to meet Rosie yet? #$b# She actually can talk to me now, I think that's progress!$1",
"RobinRosalieArrivalCT2": "Rosalie seemed surprised I already knew about her situation... #$b# I hope I didn't offend her...$2",

"Robin.RosalieGeorgeWCCT": "Is she disabled enough to use a wheelchair or able bodied enough to walk?$3 #$b#People should mind their own business and not assume the worst.$3",

"Robin.RosaliesFlareUpEventCT": "I told Gus for years that Rosalie's husband was a boy. She needs a man to care for her.$3 #$e# Sebastian's dad and I weren't happy. I didn't realize how lucky I was that he was understanding of that throughout the whole process.$2 #$e# I wish Rosie's ex was honest about his feelings for her. Maybe she'd be hurting less if he had...$2",


"Robin.RosalieDreamsAndDisastersCT": "Rosalie and Shane have always been close. Like brother and sister. #$b# But as they got older, they had a spark of something more between them.$1 #$e# All I'll say is Shane would be crazy not to be interested in Rosalie. I mean, she's gorgeous!$1 #$e# I did wonder what would have happened if Rosie and Shane had gone to the same high school though...$2",
"Robin.RosalieShaneSleepOverCT": "Demetrius noticed something was off with Rosie when we were at the saloon last...$2 #$b# I thought he was just imagining it, but Rosie seemed to be in tears when Shane took her into the back...$2 #$b# I'm glad Rosie has her best friend back. Looks like nothing's changed!$1 #$e# I wish Demetrius was as in tune with my emotions as he was with her's...$3",
"Robin.RosalieShaneSecondFirstKissCT": "I tried to ask Rosalie what was going on lately with her and Shane, but she hasn't been opening up to me like she used to...$2 #$e# I know I'm not her mother, but if he did something to hurt her, he's going to have some words with my favorite axe.$m #$e# I was kidding!$4 #$b# or was I?$2",

/*
