*/
"SamRosalieRamp": "A ramp?! No way!$h #$b# I can't wait to use it to skateboard into the saloon!",
"SamRosalieArrivalCT": "Rumour has it the new girl has a good voice. #$b# But I heard her talk, it's nothing special.$s",

"Sam.RosalieRadioEventCT": "I have to admit, I was wrong! #$b# Rosalie has some pipes!$1 #$e# Do you think Rosalie would join my band?",
"Sam.RosalieTheWinterMermaidEventCT": "Now that Rosalie's been discovered, I guess it's a bit late to ask her to join my band, huh...$s",

