"Sandy.RosalieRadioEventCT": "I heard your interview on the radio! #$b# It seems like you and the Stardew Valley Rose are quite close!$1",

"Sandy.RosalieTheWinterMermaidCT": "Emily's mermaid friend has quite the voice! #$b# I heard she's quite the local celebrity!$h",

