"Sebastian.RosalieGeorgeWCCT": "My mom's been ranting about the thing with George. #$b# She keeps talking about what *she* would have done, but honestly, I would have ran too... #$b# Or, wheeled away.$h,",

"Sebastian.RosaliesFlareUpEventCT": "$query PLAYER_NPC_RELATIONSHIP Dating Engaged Married#Huh. That sucks for the new girl. #$e# People can be genuine, but not honest. #$e# And yet, people ask why I prefer to be alone.$s|Huh. That sucks for the new girl. #$e# People can be genuine, but not honest. #$e# And yet, people ask why I prefer to be alone.$s #$b# Except you, of course.$1",
