"Willy.RosalieTheWinterMermaidCT": "Ah! So, the Night Market Mermaid has decided to sail to another of the seven seas. #$b# How wonderful our local siren gets her voice.$1",


/*Wizard*/
"WizardRosalieArrivalCT": "Something... has changed... #$b# The winds... They're carrying a sound... #$e# I must observe this change.", 
"WizardRosalieArrivalCT_OneWeek": "She appears younger than she is... It can't just be good genetics...",
"WizardRosalieArrivalCT_TwoWeeks": "I have my suspicions... but I'll need more time to observe the girl.",
"WizardRosalieArrivalCT_FourWeeks": "She doesn't appear to be evil, though her voice appears to attract many. She was right to keep silent as a child.",
"WizardRosalieArrivalCT_EightWeeks": "The Doctor... The Rose... The Farm Boy... #$b# There's something I must be missing...",

"Wizard.RosaliesStoryCT": "They say she lived near the ocean... 'Somewhere across the sea'... #$b# I cannot rule out that the girl doesn't have some magical properties to her. #$b# If she stays, I will continue my research.",
"Wizard.RosaliesFlareUpEventCT": "So, she's going through a divorce... does she know a good lawyer? #$b# I'm uh asking for a friend.",
"Wizard.RosaliesFlareUpEventCT_OneWeek": "The Rose and the Doctor have something going on. But it's not my place to say. #$e# It's a little out of character even for him.",
"Wizard.RosalieRadioEventCT1": "A child has been spreading rumours about the Rose girl. #$b# I'm unsure to put an end to her fantasies, or to consider them.",
"Wizard.RosalieRadioEventCT2": "There is always some truth in every story we hear. #$b# Even those of fiction. #$b# I don't think the child, or any of us have any reason to fear her.",

"Wizard.ShaneRosalieLowDayCT": "She's good with animals? Except a certain chicken? That's hardly news.",
"Wizard.RosaliexShane": "I can't put my finger on it but... something just isn't right about the Rose and the Farm Boy being together... #$b# It's nothing personal. Just... something is wrong... like the fates are saying it's not right... #$e# I wish the fates would have said the same thing about me and my ex wife. #$e# Why would I say something? Sometimes soulmates are friends and nothing more. If they want to be, that's on them.",

"Wizard.RosalieTheWinterMermaidCT":"She's playing the mermaid for the Night Market? #$b# Oh. That's just coincidence. #$e# What?",

